  i3 Keybinding Cheat Sheet
  ═══════════════════════════════════════

  CORE
  ────────────────────────────────────────
  Super+Return          Open terminal
  Super+q               Kill focused window
  Super+d               App launcher (rofi)
  Super+Tab             Window switcher
  Super+c               Clipboard history
  Super+p / Print       Screenshot
  F1                    This cheat sheet

  FOCUS
  ────────────────────────────────────────
  Super+h/j/k/l         Focus left/down/up/right
  Super+Arrow keys      Focus left/down/up/right
  Super+a               Focus parent container
  Super+Space           Toggle focus tiled/floating

  MOVE WINDOWS
  ────────────────────────────────────────
  Super+Shift+h/j/k/l   Move window
  Super+Shift+Arrows     Move window
  Hold Super + drag      Move floating window

  LAYOUT
  ────────────────────────────────────────
  Super+b               Split horizontal
  Super+v               Split vertical
  Super+s               Stacking layout
  Super+w               Tabbed layout
  Super+e               Toggle split
  Super+f               Fullscreen
  Super+Shift+Space     Toggle floating

  WORKSPACES
  ────────────────────────────────────────
  Super+1-9,0           Switch workspace
  Super+Shift+1-9,0     Move to workspace

  SCRATCHPAD
  ────────────────────────────────────────
  Super+Shift+minus     Send to scratchpad
  Super+minus           Show scratchpad

  RESIZE MODE
  ────────────────────────────────────────
  Super+r               Enter resize mode
  h/j/k/l or Arrows     Resize (in mode)
  Escape / Return       Exit resize mode

  SESSION
  ────────────────────────────────────────
  Super+Shift+c         Reload config
  Super+Shift+r         Restart i3
  Super+Shift+e         Power menu
  Super+Shift+x         Lock screen
  Super+Shift+p         Power profile switcher

  MEDIA
  ────────────────────────────────────────
  Volume Up/Down        Adjust volume (5%)
  Super+Volume Up/Down  Fine volume (1%)
  Mute                  Toggle mute
  Brightness Up/Down    Adjust brightness
  Play/Pause            Media toggle
  Next/Prev             Media skip
